- IProfessional interface: { id: string; specialty: string; userId: string }
- IClinicProfessional interface: { clinicId: string; professionalId: string }
- IAuthTokens interface: { accessToken: string }
- ILoginStandardDto interface: { email: string; password: string }
- ILoginAttendantDto interface: { clinicId: string; username: string; password: string }

Export everything from packages/types/src/index.ts.

